description: Slammin’ Sliders Truck, which serves a Kobe-Wagyu beef slider, a Niman Ranch pork slider, a chipotle chicken slider, a shrimp po’ boy slider and a pink pepper–crusted lobster slider. Just to keep things interesting, there are also Black Angus beef renditions of a Philly cheesesteak and a bulgogi sandwich. ”Slammin’ sides” include options like a sweet potato and pepper-jack croquette and an Okinawan-style potato salad. There’s even Caffe D’Amore coffee to wash it down!
name: Slammin Sliders
